        <p class="f-ua fs13">My name is Oleksii, I am 23. Before the war, I studied at university as a photographer and was engaged in creative work professionally. I made a living shooting music videos and photos, but on February 24, 2022 I lost it all, as well as many people in my country. Some have lost loved ones, some have lost everything they had saved and kept for decades, everything that was close to their hearts. We all lost it in an instant.<br><br>A short story about myself, I am from a small town Lubny, Poltava region, in 2019 I moved to the capital of Ukraine, Kyiv, here I went to university, which I dreamed to go to. In this city I managed to save up for a camera, which I wanted for a long time, lenses, stabilizer for video. I overcame the coronavirus, I adapted to the new realities of quarantine, I shot and survived, that's my bread. Well, you all know the story from February 24th, wherever you are, you heard about us and our troubles.<br><br>The aggressor will pay for everything, for all the death and pain he brought to our land, only we will not be broken, together we will win. All we need now is the support of others. Glory to Ukraine!<br><br><b>LOST</b>: <a class="link-btn" href="https://www.sony.ua/image/beb647675eb9d4bd499ce4b1e66583d5?fmt=jpeg&wid=2880&qlt=43" target="_blank">Sony A7III</a> <a class="link-btn" href="https://fotosale.ua/images/products/63/products.63145.1.b.jpg" target="_blank">Sigma 24mm</a> <a class="link-btn" href="https://fotosale.ua/images/products/51/products.51785.1.b.jpg" target="_blank">Sigma 85mm</a> <a class="link-btn" href="https://fotomost.com.ua/content/images/20/1800x1800l80mc0/dji-ronin-sc-31844621370933.webp" target="_blank">DJI Ronin SC</a></p>
